turns.utterance: Sushi is my all time favorite food.
turns.response: Sushi usually comes with brown or white rice. Which do you prefer?

turns.utterance: It doesn't really matter. White rice will do.
turns.response: white rice is good when cooked well, it's also the third-largest in production in the world

turns.utterance: Wow, i didn't know white rice was so popular.
turns.response: Absolutely, its the most consumed grain by humans.

turns.utterance: I think it's because it's cheap and when combined with beans makes a complete protein.
turns.response: Beans and rice is a great dish by itself or can be combined with chicken, pork, or beef.
